 style=\"text-align: center;\">Exercise</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Light to moderate</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Fluid intake</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Women 2 litres Men 2.5 litres</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Kate Morgan Lifestyle</h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/06/plan3.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-137\" src=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/06/plan3.png\" alt=\"plan3\" width=\"124\" height=\"124\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">The lifestyle plan adds an additional formulated meal replacement and one serve of carbohydrates to the evening meal. The end result is still rapid weight loss, but also a high level of satiety. For many people the lifestyle plan will actually provide more rapid results than the standard plan.</p>\n<a> Eating Plan </a>\n<table id=\"program-details\" style=\"height: auto;\" width=\"100%\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Suitable BMI</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">25+</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Calories per day</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Women 800 Men 1000</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Number of KM meal replacement per day</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Women 3 Men 3</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Supplementation required?</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Yes</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Average duration</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">8 Weeks</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Exercise</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Light only</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Fluid intake</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align