 Creme pack contains 14 x 52 g Chocolate European Meal<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">  </span>Replacement<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">  </span>cremes Kate Morgan Meal Replacement Creme sachets are heavily fortified with all of the vitamins and minerals that your body needs to stay healthy while you lose weight. <span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">  </span>They are part of a nutritionally balanced weight loss program and taste great, keeping you fuller for longer.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">  </span>Contents of one sachet replaces one meal.</p>','publish','closed','closed','','vanilla-european-creme-7-day-pack','','','2015-08-10 16:41:04','2015-08-10 06:41:04','',0,'http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/product/vanilla-european-creme-7-day-pack/',3,'product','',0),(602,1,'2015-07-29 14:29:14','2015-07-29 04:29:14','<h3 class=\"widget-title\">Simone – lost 17 kg</h3>\r\n<table style=\"width: 100%;\" border=\"0\">\r\n<thead>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th class=\"bfandaft\">Before</th>\r\n<th class=\"bfandaft\">After</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n</thead>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\" valign=\"top\"><a href=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/07/unnamed-7.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-595\" src=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/07/unnamed-7-208x300.jpg\" alt=\"unnamed-7\" width=\"208\" height=\"300\" /></a></td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\" valign=\"top\"><a href=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/07/unnamed-6.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-594\" src=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/07/unnamed-6-134x300.jpg\" alt=\"unnamed-6\" width=\"134\" height=\"300\" /></a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n\" I Found Kate Morgan very easy, mainly because I was determined to lose the weight and because Jan, my consultant, was so helpful. She was so supportive and always had the right words if I had a bit of a slow week. The shakes were quick and easy to prepare and I also love the fact that as I was losing the weight, friends commented on how good I was looking and asked me how I did it. I had no hesitation in telling them Kate Morgan and how easy it was. So far to date I have had about 6 friends join up with I think is fantastic.\"\r\n<h3 class=\"widget-title\">Amanda – lost 27.2 kg</h3>\r\n<table style=\"width: 100%;\" border=\"0\">\r\n<thead>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th class=\"bfandaft\">Before</th>\r\n<th class=\"bfandaft\">After</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n</thead>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\" valign=\"top\"> <img class=\"alignnone wp-image-581 size-full\" src=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/07/Amanda-before.jpg\" alt=\"Amanda before\" width=\"140\" height=\"245\" /></td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\" valign=\"top\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-580 size-full\" src=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/07/unnamed-2.jpg\" alt=\"unnamed-2\" width=\"122\" height=\"275\" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n\" I saw the KM advertisement in the local paper and a few days after I actually went to go and buy some jeans. I didn\'t like the size of the jeans I was going to buy, so I went into the chemist and asked for info on the kate Morgan program and I ended up joining. At first I found it hard to get used to having no carbs, which I basically lived on, but once you get past that it\'s quite easy. It fits in with my lifestyle, working, looking after my daughter, etc. It was a good incentive getting weighed in each week to stick to it and the encouragement from the staff was great.\"\r\n\r\nAmanda, Whyalla Stuart, SA\r\n<h3 class=\"widget-title\">Mandi – lost 21.2 kg</h3>\r\n<table style=\"width: 100%;\" border=\"0\">\r\n<thead>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th class=\"bfandaft\">Before</th>\r\n<th class=\"bfandaft\">After</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n</thead>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\" valign=\"top\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-584 size-full\" src=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/07/Mandi-McFarlane-Before.jpg\" alt=\"Mandi McFarlane Before\" width=\"112\" height=\"230\" /></td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\" valign=\"top\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-583\" src=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/07/unnamed-3.jpg\" alt=\"unnamed-3\" width=\"140\" height=\"210\" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n\"With fantastic support along the way, Kate Morgan has made my challenge easy and enjoyable, something that I couldn\'t achieve on my own.  It has been a life changing experience.  I now feel so much better about myself and have regained my shattered conference.  I am excited to be an inspiration to others.\"\r\n<h3 class=\"widget-title\">Justin lost 36.1kg in 44 weeks</h3>\r\n<table style=\"width: 100%;\" border=\"0\">\r\n<thead>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th class=\"bfandaft\">Before</th>\r\n<th class=\"bfandaft\">After</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n</thead>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\" valign=\"top\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-587\" src=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/07/Justin-Benn-before-web.png\" alt=\"Justin Benn before web\" width=\"197\" height=\"380\" /></td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\" valign=\"top\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-586 size-full\" src=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/07/unnamed-4.jpg\" alt=\"unnamed-4\" width=\"278\" height=\"418\" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n\"I have always been a bit overweight and never throught i could achieve the results i have, I couldn\'t have done it without the wonderful support of the staff at Kate Morgan. Thanks Ladies\"\r\nJustin- QLD\r\n<h3 class=\"widget-title\">Jacklyn – lost 12.1 kg</h3>\r\n<table style=\"width: 100%;\" border=\"0\">\r\n<thead>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th class=\"bf