15-08-05 13:08:45','2015-08-05 03:08:45','<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Simone lost 17 kg</h3>\r\n<table width=\"100%\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><strong>Before</strong></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><strong>After</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><a href=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/07/unnamed-7.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-595\" src=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/07/unnamed-7-208x300.jpg\" alt=\"unnamed-7\" width=\"208\" height=\"300\" /></a></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><a href=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/07/unnamed-6.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-594\" src=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/07/unnamed-6-134x300.jpg\" alt=\"unnamed-6\" width=\"134\" height=\"300\" /></a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: justify;\" colspan=\"2\">\"I Found Kate Morgan very easy, mainly because I was determined to lose the weight and because Jan, my consultant, was so helpful. She was so supportive and always had the right words if I had a bit of a slow week. The shakes were quick and easy to prepare and I also love the fact that as I was losing the weight, friends commented on how good I was looking and asked me how I did it. I had no hesitation in telling them Kate Morgan and how easy it was. So far to date I have had about 6 friends join up with I think is fantastic.\"</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Amanda lost 27.2 kg</h3>\r\n<table width=\"100%\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><strong>Before</strong></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><strong>After</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-581 size-full\" src=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/07/Amanda-before.jpg\" alt=\"Amanda before\" width=\"140\" height=\"245\" /></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-580\" src=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/07/unnamed-2.jpg\" alt=\"unnamed-2\" width=\"122\" height=\"275\" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: justify;\" colspan=\"2\">\n\n\" I saw the KM advertisement in the local paper and a few days after I actually went to go and buy some jeans. I didn\'t like the size of the jeans I was going to buy, so I went into the chemist and asked for info on the kate Morgan program and I ended up joining. At first I found it hard to get used to having no carbs, which I basically lived on, but once you get past that it\'s quite easy. It fits in with my lifestyle, working, looking after my daughter, etc. It was a good incentive getting weighed in each week to stick to it and the encouragement from the staff was great.\"\r\n\r\nAmanda, Whyalla Stuart, SA</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Mandi lost 21.2 kg</h3>\r\n<table width=\"100%\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><strong>Before</strong></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><strong>After</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-584 size-full\" src=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/07/Mandi-McFarlane-Before.jpg\" alt=\"Mandi McFarlane Before\" width=\"112\" height=\"230\" /></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-583\" src=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/07/unnamed-3.jpg\" alt=\"unnamed-3\" width=\"140\" height=\"210\" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: justify;\" colspan=\"2\">\"With fantastic support along the way, Kate Morgan has made my challenge easy and enjoyable, something that I couldn\'t achieve on my own.  It has been a life changing experience.  I now feel so much better about myself and have regained my shattered conference.  I am excited to be an inspiration to others.\"</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Justin lost 36.1kg</h3>\r\n<table width=\"100%\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><strong>Before</strong></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><strong>After</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-587 size-medium\" src=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/07/Justin-Benn-before-web-156x300.png\" alt=\"Justin Benn before web\" width=\"156\" height=\"300\" /></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-586\" src=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/07/unnamed-4-200x300.jpg\" alt=\"unnamed-4\" width=\"200\" height=\"300\" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: justify;\" colspan=\"2\">\"I have always been a bit overweight and never throught i could achieve the results i have, I couldn\'t have done it without the wonderful support of the staff at Kate Morgan. Thanks Ladies\" Justin- QLD</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Trinna lost 54 kg</h3>\r\n<table width=\"100%\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><strong>Before</strong></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><strong>After</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-592\" src=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/07/Trinna-before.jpg\" alt=\"Trinna before\" width=\"140\" height=\"231\" /></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><a href=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/07/Trinna-After.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-591\" src=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/07/Trinna-After.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"137\" height=\"275\" /></a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: justify;\" colspan=\"2\">\"Kate Morgan has helped by giving me a balanced diet to which I was able to stick to and achieve my goals by helping my health and making me feel better about myself.   I am much more energetic and happy.\"</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Larissa lost 28.8kg</h3>\r\n<table width=\"100%\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><strong>Before</strong></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><strong>After</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><a href=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/07/Larissa-afte.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-621\" src=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/07/Larissa-afte.jpg\" alt=\"Larissa afte\" width=\"100\" height=\"275\" /></a></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><a href=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/07/Larissa-faulkner-Before-web.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-622\" src=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/07/Larissa-faulkner-Before-web.jpg\" alt=\"Larissa faulkner Before web\" width=\"140\" height=\"236\" /></a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: justify;\" colspan=\"2\">\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">\"Kate Morgan has helped me achieve a healthier and happier lifestyle.  After losing so much weight I feel like a different person.  I found with the help of Kate Morgan, my friends and family, I was able to achieve my goals with ease.  I recommend Kate Morgan to anyone who is looking to live a healthier lifestyle\".</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Damla lost 21kg</h3>\r\n<table width=\"100%\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><strong>Before</strong></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><strong>After</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><a href=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/07/Damla-Before_web.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-623\" src=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/07/Damla-Before_web.jpg\" alt=\"Damla Before_web\" width=\"116\" height=\"275\" /></a></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><a href=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/07/Damla-After_web.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-624\" src=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/07/Damla-After_web.jpg\" alt=\"Damla After_web\" width=\"122\" height=\"275\" /></a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: justify;\" colspan=\"2\">\"Kate Morgan has helped me control my calorie intake, lose weight and maintain weight.  I feel healthier and can now control my food intake.  Thank you Kate Morgan.\"</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Damla lost 21kg</h3>\r\n<table width=\"100%\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><strong>Before</strong></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><strong>After</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><a href=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/07/lise-playford-before-.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-639\" src=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/07/lise-playford-before--97x300.jpg\" alt=\"lise - playford before\" width=\"97\" height=\"300\" /></a></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><a href=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/07/unnamed-21.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-640\" src=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/07/unnamed-21-180x300.jpg\" alt=\"unnamed-2\" width=\"180\" height=\"300\" /></a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: justify;\" colspan=\"2\">\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\"Kate Morgan kept me on the straight and narrow, knowing I was going to get weighed every week.  The shakes were so easy because I didn\'t have to worry about what I was going to eat.  Kate Morgan staff were so helpful and encouraging.  It was always a pleasure to deal with them.\"</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Todd lost 29.3kg</h3>\r\n<table width=\"100%\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><strong>Before</strong></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><strong>After</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"> <a href=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/07/todd-before.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-644\" src=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/07/todd-before-184x300.jpg\" alt=\"todd before\" width=\"184\" height=\"300\" /></a></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"> <a href=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/07/todd_after.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-645\" src=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/07/todd_after-193x300.png\" alt=\"todd_after\" width=\"193\" height=\"300\" /></a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: justify;\" colspan=\"2\">\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\"Kate Morgan has helped me achieve not only my weight loss goals but my confidence goals. I now look at the program not as weight loss but a life style change. For the first time in my life I now wear belts with all my new jeans. I finally fit into clothes that I bought 4 years ago. It\'s such a great feeling not having to shop in the \"MR BIG\" section and buying clothes with the dreaded \"XXL\"symbols. Everyday, I look in the mirror and can\'t believe my achievements. My friends and family are in even more disbelief than I am. For once, I have found something that works for me and is easy to manage around a busy lifestyle.\"</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Ross lost 20.6kg</h3>\r\n<table width=\"100%\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><strong>Before</strong></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><strong>After</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-651 size-full\" src=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/07/ross-before_web.jpg\" alt=\"ross before_web\" width=\"134\" height=\"275\" /></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"> <img class=\"alignnone wp-i