.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/07/Seared-Beef-Salad_71-A--300x200.jpg\" alt=\"Seared Beef Salad_71 A\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Ingredients</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n<div class=\"ingredients\">120g sirloin steak (or other)</div></li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<div class=\"ingredients\">100g thin green beans, blanched and refreshed</div></li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<div class=\"ingredients\">100g thin butter beans, blanched and refreshed</div></li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<div class=\"ingredients\">1/2 cup cherry tomatoes, halved</div></li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<div class=\"ingredients\">1/2 red onion, sliced thinly</div></li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<div class=\"ingredients\">2 cloves garlic mashed together with 1/2 teaspoon salt</div></li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<div class=\"ingredients\">2 tablespoons flat leaf parsley</div></li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<div class=\"cost\">2 tablespoons fat free french dressing</div></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div class=\"cost\"><strong>Method</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"cost\">\r\n<p class=\"Method\">Rub garlic mixture all over steak and rest for 10 mins.</p>\r\n<p class=\"Method\">Barbecue on grill until cooked to your liking. Set aside.</p>\r\n<p class=\"Method\">Toss all other ingredients together with french dressing.</p>\r\n<p class=\"Method\">Slice steak thinly and gently fold through salad.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>','Steak Salad','','inherit','open','open','','442-revision-v1','','','2015-08-06 14:28:51','2015-08-06 04:28:51','',442,'http://174.121.78.227/442-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(772,1,'2015-08-06 14:31:08','2015-08-06 04:31:08','','Beef Stew_19 A','','inherit','open','open','','beef-stew_19-a','','','2015-08-06 14:31:08','2015-08-06 04:31:08','',445,'http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/07/Beef-Stew_19-A.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(773,1,'2015-08-06 14:32:00','2015-08-06 04:32:00','<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-772\" src=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/07/Beef-Stew_19-A-300x200.jpg\" al