','open','','762-autosave-v1','','','2015-08-06 14:36:17','2015-08-06 04:36:17','',762,'http://174.121.78.227/762-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(779,1,'2015-08-06 14:37:49','2015-08-06 04:37:49','<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-780\" src=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/08/Beef-shaslik.jpg\" alt=\"Beef shaslik\" width=\"270\" height=\"142\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Ingredients</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>120 g porterhouse steak, cut into cubes</li>\r\n	<li>cherry tomatoes</li>\r\n	<li>zucchini, cut into chunks</li>\r\n	<li>spring onions, cut into batons</li>\r\n	<li>red capsicum, cut into pieces</li>\r\n	<li>bamboo skewers</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Method</strong>\r\n\r\nThread beef onto bamboo skewers and alternate with tomato, zucchini, spring onion and capsicum.\r\n\r\nSprinkle with curry powder and BBQ on hot plate until brown on all sides and cooked through.\r\n\r\nServe with yoghurt dressing.','Beef Shaslik','','publish','closed','closed','','beef-shaslik','','','2015-08-06 14:37:49','2015-08-06 04:37:49','',396,'http://174.121.78.227/?page_id=779',0,'page','',0),(780,1,'2015-08-06 14:37:34','2015-08-06 04:37:34','','Beef shaslik','','inherit','open','open','','beef-shaslik','','','2015-08-06 14:37:34','2015-08-06 04:37:34','',779,'http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/08/Beef-shaslik.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(781,1,'2015-08-06 14:37:49','2015-08-06 04:37:49','<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-780\" src=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/08/Beef-shaslik.jpg\" alt=\"Beef shaslik\" width=\"270\" height=\"142\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Ingredients</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>120 g porterhouse steak, cut into cubes</li>\r\n	<li>cherry tomatoes</li>\r\n	<li>zucchini, cut into chunks</li>\r\n	<li>spring onions, cut into batons</li>\r\n	<li>red capsicum, cut into pieces</li>\r\n	<li>bamboo skewers</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Method</strong>\r\n\r\nThread beef onto bamboo skewers and al