s, phone number, email address etc. is only accessible from our website after supplying a username and password. In order to operate our website effectively, or to deliver products and services to you, we may pass on your personal information to our partners including Terry White Chemists from time to time.\r\n<h3>Access and correction of Personal Information</h3>\r\nYou may contact us at any time to make a request to access your personal information. The request may be made to us by telephone, fax, email, or post, the contact details of which are provided at the end of this Privacy Policy. We may charge a reasonable fee to you for providing access to such personal information in circumstances where considerable time is involved in locating, collating and providing the requested information to you.\r\n\r\nIf any of the personal information which we hold about you is inaccurate, incomplete in any way or you would like us to update the personal information which we hold about you, you may make a request for us to correct your personal information which we will attend to as soon as it is reasonably practicable to do so.\r\n<h3>Cookies</h3>\r\nFor added convenience, we have employed a “cookie” system for our website. A “cookie” is a small temporary file stored on a user’s hard drive which lets our website store information about that user in order to better tailor our website to your needs and interests. This information allows us to make our website easier to use and may assist the user by saving time, e.g. the user will not be required to continually enter their password or ‘sign in’ again upon return visits to the website. Cookies allow our servers to keep track of customer details between visits to our website.\r\n\r\nThe information stored by the cookie includes the data that is provided during online registration. This information is only accessible online when a customer enters their username and password. Other information stored by a cookie includes website traffic data. This is not used to identify individual details but only collated into aggregate anonymous results in order to evaluate and improve our shopping service for our customers.\r\n\r\nCredit Card Information is never stored in the cookie.\r\n\r\nYou do not have to accept cookies in order to use our website and you may adjust your web browser in order to be notified when you receive a cookie or to reject cookies, however if you choose to reject cookies there may be some loss of functionality of our website and convenience of product and other offerings to you.\r\n<h3>Email Addresses</h3>\r\nWe will store your email address if you send us a query, place an order or subscribe to an email list. Your email address is used for the purpose you provide it for and statistical information only, and is never disclosed to any third parties for any other purpose without your consent.\r\n<h3>Spam</h3>\r\nWe will never knowingly send you electronic messages without your consent, however we may send you information about the products and services that we offer, opportunities that may be of benefit to you and the like. You may inform us at any time if you do not wish to receive any such information from us.\r\n<h3>Data Security</h3>\r\nWe will take all reasonable steps to preserve the privacy of your personal information. Our order processing system is protected by a firewall, when you make an online purchase from us. A firewall is a hardware and software security system designed to filter specified exchanges of information and restrict access to authorised systems and users. When you place an order online our website encrypts and passes all of the order information supplied to our back-office system, which is not connected directly to the internet.\r\n\r\nCrucially, unencrypted credit card details will not be stored on our server, and will be sent only in encrypted form. The encryption technology we use is the industry standard SSL (Secure Socket Layers).\r\n<h3>Where are our servers located?</h3>\r\nThe Personal Information which you provide to us may be stored on our contractor’s servers that may be from time to time located outside of Australia.\r\n\r\nWe are able to extract any data stored on overseas servers on to our servers as a back up on a regular basis.\r\n<h3>Transfer of Your Personal Information</h3>\r\nWe will only transfer your personal information to a business advisor, contractor or related entity whether in Australia or in a foreign country if the transfer is to a recipient that has covenanted to be bound by this Policy and that is subject to a law or contract which upholds the principles for the fair handling of personal information in a manner similar to the National Privacy Principles or you consent to the transfer or the transfer is necessary for the performance of providing contracted products or services to you or we have taken reasonable steps to ensure that the personal information which is to be transferred will not be held, used or disclosed by the recipient of the information in any way which is inconsistent with the National Privacy Principles.\r\n<h3>Changes to this Privacy Policy</h3>\r\nKate Morgan Weight loss may be required to change the terms of this Privacy Policy from time to time due to changing business requirements or changes in the law. Kate Morgan Weigh loss reserves the right to change the Privacy Policy at any time and any changes effected to the Privacy Policy by us will be included in the updated Privacy Policy appearing on this website under the privacy policy link.\r\n\r\nContinued use of the website by you is deemed acceptance of the amended terms of the Privacy Policy.\r\n<h3>Feedback and Complaints Handling Procedure</h3>\r\nWe welcome your feedback and will attend to all complaints received by you promptly and in a proper manner. Please email, fax or write to our Privacy Officer using the contact information below.\r\n\r\nIf you are unable to resolve your concern or query with our Privacy Officer, you may contact the Federal Privacy Commissioner regarding lodging of a complaint. The Commissioner’s website is www.privacy.gov.au or the telephone number is 1300 363 992.\r\n<h3>Who to Contact if you have any Privacy Concerns or Queries</h3>\r\nIf you have any questions about our Privacy Policy or the manner in which we deal with your personal information, please contact us\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','Privacy Policy','','inherit','open','open','','221-revision-v1','','','2015-08-13 09:37:22','2015-08-12 23:37:22','',221,'http://174.121.78.227/221-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(927,1,'2015-08-13 09:40:17','2015-08-12 23:40:17','<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Simone</h3>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">lost 17 kg</h3>\r\n<table width=\"100%\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><strong>Before</strong></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><strong>After</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><a href=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/07/unnamed-7.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-595\" src=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/07/unnamed-7-208x300.jpg\" alt=\"unnamed-7\" width=\"208\" height=\"300\" /></a></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><a href=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/07/unnamed-6.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-594\" src=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/07/unnamed-6-134x300.jpg\" alt=\"unnamed-6\" width=\"134\" height=\"300\" /></a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: justify;\" colspan=\"2\">\"I Found Kate Morgan very easy, mainly because I was determined to lose the weight and because Jan, my consultant, was so helpful. She was so supportive and always had the right words if I had a bit of a slow week. The shakes were quick and easy to prepare and I also love the fact that as I was losing the weight, friends commented on how good I was looking and asked me how I did it. I had no hesitation in telling them Kate Morgan and how easy it was. So far to date I have had about 6 friends join up with I think is fantastic.\"</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Amanda</h3>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">lost 27.2 kg</h3>\r\n<table width=\"100%\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><strong>Before</strong></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><strong>After</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-581 size-full\" src=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/07/Amanda-before.jpg\" alt=\"Amanda before\" width=\"140\" height=\"245\" /></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-580\" src=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/07/unnamed-2.jpg\" alt=\"unnamed-2\" width=\"122\" height=\"275\" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: justify;\" colspan=\"2\">\n\n\" I saw the KM advertisement in the local paper and a few days after I actually went to go and buy some jeans. I didn\'t like the size of the jeans I was going to buy, so I went into the chemist and asked for info on the kate Morgan program and I ended up joining. At first I found it hard to get used to having no carbs, which I basically lived on, but once you get past that it\'s quite easy. It fits in with my lifestyle, working, looking after my daughter, etc. It was a good incentive getting weighed in each week to stick to it and the encouragement from the staff was great.\"\r\n\r\nAmanda, Whyalla Stuart, SA</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Mandi</h3>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">lost 21.2 kg</h3>\r\n<table width=\"100%\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><strong>Before</strong></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><strong>After</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-584 size-full\" src=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/07/Mandi-McFarlane-Before.jpg\" alt=\"Mandi McFarlane Before\" width=\"112\" height=\"230\" /></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-583\" src=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/07/unnamed-3.jpg\" alt=\"unnamed-3\" width=\"140\" height=\"210\" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: justify;\" colspan=\"2\">\"With fantastic support along the way, Kate Morgan has made my challenge easy and enjoyable, something that I couldn\'t achieve on my own.  It has been a life changing experience.  I now feel so much better about myself and have regained my shattered conference.  I am excited to be an inspiration to others.\"</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Justin</h3>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">lost 36.1kg</h3>\r\n<table width=\"100%\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><strong>Before</strong></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><strong>After</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-587 size-medium\" src=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/07/Justin-Benn-before-web-156x300.png\" alt=\"Justin Benn before web\" width=\"156\" height=\"300\" /></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-586\" src=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/07/unnamed-4-200x300.jpg\" alt=\"unnamed-4\" width=\"200\" height=\"300\" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: justify;\" colspan=\"2\">\"I have always been a bit overweight and never throught i could achieve the results i have, I couldn\'t have done it without the wonderful support of the staff at Kate Morgan. Thanks Ladies\"\r\nJustin- QLD</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Trinna</h3>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">lost 54 kg</h3>\r\n<table width=\"100%\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><strong>Before</strong></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><strong>After</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-592\" src=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/07/Trinna-before.jpg\" alt=\"Trinna before\" width=\"140\" height=\"231\" /></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><a href=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/07/Trinna-After.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-591\" src=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/07/Trinna-After.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"137\" height=\"275\" /></a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: justify;\" colspan=\"2\">\"Kate Morgan has helped by giving me a balanced diet to which I was able to stick to and achieve my goals by helping my health and making me feel better about myself.   I am much more energetic and happy.\"</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Larissa lost 28.8kg</h3>\r\n<table width=\"100%\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><strong>Before</strong></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><strong>After</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><a href=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/07/Larissa-afte.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-621\" src=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/07/Larissa-afte.jpg\" alt=\"Larissa afte\" width=\"100\" height=\"275\" /></a></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><a href=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/07/Larissa-faulkner-Before-web.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-622\" src=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/07/Larissa-faulkner-Before-web.jpg\" alt=\"Larissa faulkner Before web\" width=\"140\" height=\"236\" /></a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: justify;\" colspan=\"2\">\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">\"Kate Morgan has helped me achieve a healthier and happier lifestyle.  After losing so much weight I feel like a different person.  I found with the help of Kate Morgan, my friends and family, I was able to achieve my goals with ease.  I recommend Kate Morgan to anyone who is looking to live a healthier lifestyle\".</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Damla</h3>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">lost 21kg</h3>\r\n<table width=\"100%\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><strong>Before</strong></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><strong>After</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><a href=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/07/Damla-Before_web.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-623\" src=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/07/Damla-Before_web.jpg\" alt=\"Damla Before_web\" width=\"116\" height=\"275\" /></a></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><a href=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/07/Damla-After_web.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-624\" src=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/07/Damla-After_web.jpg\" alt=\"Damla After_web\" width=\"122\" height=\"275\" /></a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: justify;\" colspan=\"2\">\"Kate Morgan has helped me control my calorie intake, lose weight and maintain weight.  I feel healthier and can now control my food intake.  Thank you Kate Morgan.\"</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Lise</h3>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">lost 21kg</h3>\r\n<table width=\"100%\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><strong>Before</strong></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><strong>After</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><a href=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/07/lise-playford-before-.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-639\" src=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/07/lise-playford-before--97x300.jpg\" alt=\"lise - playford before\" width=\"97\" height=\"300\" /></a></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><a href=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/07/unnamed-21.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-640\" src=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/07/unnamed-21-180x300.jpg\" alt=\"unnamed-2\" width=\"180\" height=\"300\" /></a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: justify;\" colspan=\"2\">\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\"Kate Morgan kept me on the straight and narrow, knowing I was going to get weighed every week.  The shakes were so easy because I didn\'t have to worry about what I was going to eat.  Kate Morgan staff were so helpful and encouraging.  It was always a pleasure to deal with them.\"</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Todd lost 29.3kg</h3>\r\n<table width=\"100%\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><strong>Before</strong></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><strong>After</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"> <a href=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/07/todd-before.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-644\" src=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/07/todd-before-184x300.jpg\" alt=\"todd before\" width=\"184\" height=\"300\" /></a></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"> <a href=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/07/todd_after.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-645\" src=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/07/todd_after-193x300.png\" alt=\"todd_after\" width=\"193\" height=\"300\" /></a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: justify;\" colspan=\"2\">\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\"Kate Morgan has helped me achieve not only my weight loss goals but my confidence goals. I now look at the program not as weight loss but a life style change. For the first time in my life I now wear belts with all my new jeans. I finally fit into clothes that I bought 4 years ago. It\'s such a great feeling not having to shop in the \"MR BIG\" section and buying clothes with the dreaded \"XXL\"symbols. Everyday, I look in the mirror and can\'t believe my achievements. My friends and family are in even more disbelief than I am. For once, I have found something that works for me and is easy to manage around a busy lifestyle.\"</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Ross</h3>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">lost 20.6kg</h3>\r\n<table width=\"100%\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><strong>Before</strong></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><strong>After</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-651 size-full\" src=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/07/ross-before_web.jpg\" alt=\"ross before_web\" width=\"134\" height=\"275\" /></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"> <img class=\"alignnone wp-image-653 size-full\" src=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/07/ross-after_web.jpg\" alt=\"ross after_web\" width=\"119\" height=\"275\" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: justify;\" colspan=\"2\">\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\"I tried a trial pack, liked it and joined the program. I lost 10kg and was really happy with my progress and then lost another 10.6 kg. I feel heaps better for losing the weight and the staff were really supportive.\"</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n&nbsp;','Success Stories','','inherit','open','open','','575-revision-v1','','','2015-08-13 09:40:17','2015-08-12 23:40:17','',575,'http://174.121.78.227/575-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(931,1,'2015-08-13 09:49:04','2015-08-12 23:49:04','<h3>The Kate Morgan Support network</h3>\r\nWhen it comes to losing weight, we understand that support can make all of the difference. That’s way Kate Morgan is here to help you throughout your weight loss journey. Select from the following support options to best suits your needs.\r\n<h3 class=\"widget-title\">Email us</h3>\r\nIf you have any queries please email us at <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><a href=\"mailto:admin@katemorgan.com.au\">admin@katemorgan.com.au</a></span>.\r\n\r\nAll emails will be answered promptly.\r\n<h3 class=\"widget-title\">FAQ</h3>\r\nView <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><a href=\"http://174.121.78.227/faq/\">here</a></span> to see the most commonly asked questions and answers for the program.\r\n<h3 class=\"widget-title\">Facebook</h3>\r\nJoin our <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=100008878187652\">Facebook page</a></span> for extra tips, content and support.\r\n<h3 class=\"widget-title\">Forum</h3>\r\nLogin to Kate Morgan\'s forum via Facebook. Here you can chat to other members and discuss the Kate Morgan program.\r\n<h3 class=\"widget-title\">Phone our hepline</h3>\r\nCall Kate Morgan\'s trained staff on: 1300 304 570\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','Help and Support','','inherit','open','open','','820-revision-v1','','','2015-08-13 09:49:04','2015-08-12 23:49:04','',820,'http://174.121.78.227/820-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(941,1,'2015-08-13 10:03:13','2015-08-13 00:03:13','<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Which plan is best for you?</h2>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Rapid Loss Phase</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/06/plan1.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-132\" src=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/06/plan1.png\" alt=\"plan1\" width=\"124\" height=\"124\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">This is a rapid weigh loss phase, suitable for most people, but should not extend past 8 weeks. The number of calories in this plan is unlikely to leave you feeling full, but weight loss is rapid and substantial.</p>\r\n<a class=\"\" href=\"http://174.121.78.227/program/rapid-loss-phase/\"> Eating Plan </a>\r\n<table id=\"program-details\" style=\"height: auto;\" width=\"100%\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Suitable BMI</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">25+</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Calories per day</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">\n\nWomen 800\r\n\r\nMen 1000</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Number of KM meal replacement per day</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">\n\nWomen 3\r\n\r\nMen 3</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Supplementation required?</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Yes</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Average duration</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">8 Weeks</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Exercise</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Light only</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Fluid intake</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">\n\nWomen 2 litres\r\n\r\nMen 2.5 litres</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Kate Morgan Standard</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/06/plan2.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-136\" src=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/06/plan2.png\" alt=\"plan2\" width=\"124\" height=\"124\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">This plan provides a healthy balance of nutrients and is suitable for ongoing use. The plan provides rapid weight loss and restricts carbohydrates but still leaves users feeling quite satisfied.</p>\r\n<a class=\"\" href=\"http://174.121.78.227/program/standard-plan/\"> Eating Plan </a>\r\n<table id=\"program-details\" style=\"height: auto;\" width=\"100%\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Suitable BMI</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">25+</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Calories per day</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Women 1200 Men 1400</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Number of KM meal replacement per day</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Women 2 Men 3</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Supplementation required?</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">No</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Average duration</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 14px; line-height: 34px;\">Until you hit your healthy body weight</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Exercise</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Light to moderate</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Fluid intake</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Women 2 litres Men 2.5 litres</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Kate Morgan Lifestyle</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/06/plan3.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-137\" src=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/06/plan3.png\" alt=\"plan3\" width=\"124\" height=\"124\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">The lifestyle plan adds an additional formulated meal replacement and one serve of carbohydrates to the evening meal. The end result is still rapid weight loss, but also a high level of satiety. For many people the lifestyle plan will actually provide more rapid results than the standard plan.</p>\r\n<a class=\"\" href=\"http://174.121.78.227/program/lifestyle-plan/\"> Eating Plan </a>\r\n<table id=\"program-details\" style=\"height: auto;\" width=\"100%\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Suitable BMI</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">25+</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Calories per day</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Women 1600 Men 1800</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Number of KM meal replacement per day</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Women 3 Men 4</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Supplementation required?</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">No</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Average duration</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 14px; line-height: 34px;\">Until you hit your healthy body weight</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Exercise</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Light to moderate</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Fluid intake</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Women 2 litres Men 2.5 litres</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Maintenance Phase</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/06/plan4.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-138\" src=\"http://174.121.78.227/~kmxmarketing/resources/uploads/2015/06/plan4.png\" alt=\"plan4\" width=\"124\" height=\"124\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">This plan provides you with a way to calculate how much food you should consume on an ongoing basis and is suitable for everybody to explore, no matter what their current weight.</p>\r\n<a> Eating Plan </a>\r\n<table id=\"program-details\" style=\"height: auto;\" width=\"100%\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Suitable BMI</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">25+</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">C